                <h1>Grover Norquist, president of Americans for Tax Reform, advocates lower taxes at Thursday talk</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/49d900b7-c71c-40d3-a336-666c85551072.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
